owl:Ontology.dcterms:title: Credit Classification Ontology
owl:Ontology.dcterms:description: An ontology for modeling a credit classification dataset.
owl:Ontology.dcterms:creator: Lorenzo del Río

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Sex
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: The class of biological sexes, limited to the individuals Male and Female from DBpedia.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: has sex
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The biological sex of the credit requestor.
Age of the credit_requestor at the time the risk was evaluated. In years, in ISO 8601 format

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: Credit evaluation of a credit requestor
Credit evaluation of a credit requestor
Credit requestor of a credit evaluation

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: employment status of the credit requestor
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The employment status as a string: 'employed' or 'unemployed'. Refer to DBpedia for more information.
Number of persons that depend on the credit requestor

Number of other credits that the credit_requestor has
Installment rate in percentage of disposable income
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: Installment rate

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Loan info enriched with classification of the risk
owl:Class.AnnotationVocabulary1:usageNote: URIs for credit_evaluation individuals are of the form : http://data.creditclassification.biz/resource/ccf/credit_evaluation/<credit_evaluation_id> . <credit_evaluation_id> is E<integer>

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: Info of a credit requestor in the context of the evaluation of the risk of a requested loan.
owl:Class.AnnotationVocabulary1:usageNote: URIs for credit_requestor individuals are of the form : http://data.creditclassification.biz/resource/ccf/credit_requestor/<credit_requestor_id> . <credit_requestor_id> is R<integer>

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Credit history Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code providing info about the credit history of the credit requestor.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Foreign worker Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code telling if the credit requestor is foreign worker or not.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Housing Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code providing info about the housing of the credit requestor.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Job Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code providing info about the job of the credit requestor.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Other debtors guarantors Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code indicating info about other debtors/guarantors.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Other installment plans code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code indicating if the credit requestor has other installment plans.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Personal status sex code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classfication code that mixes info about the marital status and sex of the credit requestor.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Present employment Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code providing info about the present employment status of the credit requestor.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Property Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code indicating the type of property of the party.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Purpose Code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code indicating the purpose associated with a financial product or transaction.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Savings account code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code for the savings account.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Checking account code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code related to the status of the checking account.

owl:Class.rdfs:label: Telephone code
owl:Class.rdfs:comment: A classification code indicating whether the party owns a phone line or not.

rdf:Description.dcterms:title: Credit Classification Dataset
rdf:Description.dcterms:description: This RDF dataset contains structured data representing credit requestors and their associated credit evaluations for use in financial risk assessment.
